    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Persons engaged in professional or voluntary service of a specialized nature concerned with community welfare and family or social problems such as arise from poverty, mental or physical handicaps, or maladjustment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
